Text: Awooooo!!!
She is too strong! She can kill with a single blow!
Forget about magic defense! Get away!
Ack...!
Grrraaaaarrr!!!
Aghh...!
T-Too...fast...!!
Ack...!
Should you really be looking away?
Huh?!
Apostate scum, ready yourself for a real fight!
Real? like this?
Guargh...!

Even in a "real fight", if a sword strikes you from
outside of your perception, then your automatic
magic defense will be...useless.
Cat! Don't steal my prey!

I didn't steal anything. Anyway, this isn't a battle
for that kind of strategy.
What!!
Give me a break from competing today―
Ughh...

The Templar leader whistled and with that, stopped
moving.
Grr! Grrarrrr!
Did I call for you...?
You're not hunting! You're doin' something weird!

Yeah, right. Yet usually Lady Alpha is pointing out
how the stupid dog is not thorough.
This one looks...well prepared.
Awoo! A big strong one appeared!

They're really going to throw this thing into the
mix outside of church grounds...

I mean, those Templars make out their sacred
teachings to be so important.

What're you mumbling about? I'm gonna take
this one down!

Oh, that would be nice. Very kind of you to save me
the trouble.

It's not just a big ghost, it can do all kinds of
stuff. It's a hassle, so all yours.
All kinds of stuff... It can scratch with its nails?
Eek... We've got a loud one!!!

Its screams shouldn't be a problem for a stupid,
simple-minded dog...

We're in the middle of an important fight, so I don't
really want to waste my time on this one―

Hey, cat! That didn't do nothing! Try fighting a bit
more seriously!

I'm totally serious. That part I hit is its weak
point. Just to give you a rough idea, off you go.
Off I go...?

Ha-ha, I get it! You can't beat it, so you're trying
to get me to fight it?

It's not that I can't beat it, I'm just telling you
how to beat it, I guess.

I think that whistle earlier means we've got
reinforcements coming. Unlike certain dogs,
I'm not looking for strong enemies.

I don't care if you think you're the strongest today.
You take on that one, I'll take the Templars.

I think you're trying to trick me a little today,
but...

In that case, I am gonna make a trophy outta this
big one!
Yep yep, division of roles, division of roles. Now then...
Let's do this! Let's go!
